    "description": "走进《放逐大师》怪异的世界吧！这款恐怖探险游戏具有互动漫画元素，极具氛围感。你将扮演一名驱魔师兼私家侦探亚当·韦恩，接受委托的艰巨任务，举行神秘仪式，将恶魔从受害者身上赶走。你就是驱魔师。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/adbe8351076e24c92a4bd3861074bbcf.poster.avif?t=1761713663\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/adbe8351076e24c92a4bd3861074bbcf.webm?t=1761713663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驱逐附身于受害者的恶魔</h2>作为上帝的仆从，你的工作就是赶走附身于受害者的恶魔。设置陷阱，使用各种驱魔工具，为形态各异的恶魔举行独特的净仪化式。完成驱魔仪式，增加救赎的几率。在你拯救灵魂和生命的过程中，每一个仪式都至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/ab1108b782db1c3fd73fd142e245990b.poster.avif?t=1761713663\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/ab1108b782db1c3fd73fd142e245990b.webm?t=1761713663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开隐藏在阴影中的秘密</h2>踏上旅程，从生性冷漠、极度利己的侦探成长为伟大无私、乐善好施的驱魔师。完成驱魔仪式，从邪恶的侵蚀中拯救被附身的人，并推进剧情，揭示亚当·韦恩故事中最黑暗的角落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/edd453860b7197199e1625cdd76d1c2b.poster.avif?t=1761713663\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197240/extras/edd453860b7197199e1625cdd76d1c2b.webm?t=1761713663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸在极具氛围感的互动漫画中</h2>在《放逐大师》中，你所做的每一个动作和选择都将通过生动的视觉效果和惊悚刺激的互动漫画体现出来。你的故事将像热血沸腾的漫画小说一样展开，你不仅可以观察事件，还可以积极参与其中。随着你深入了解亚当的过去，这场拯救灵魂、伸张正义的战斗也愈发无法让你置身事外。<br><br>",
